response.Q0: Look at the last nodes and find the highest value. If there is a large amount of red nodes I've revealed, I will attempt to inspect the opposite side e.g. if on the top left it is all negative I will go for right side bottom nodes and explore those.
response.Q2: The randomness made it difficult as some rounds there were a large amount of red destination nodes and felt the more I spent, the less my bonus would be so I tried to spend as less as possible while obtaining the highest destination node value.
